cu.explanation_en: Setting the gNB ID to an invalid hexadecimal value will cause parsing errors and prevent the gNB from initializing.

du.explanation_en: Setting the gNB ID to an invalid hexadecimal value will cause parsing errors and prevent the gNB from initializing.
du.explanation_zh: 將 gNB ID 設定為無效的十六進位值會導致解析錯誤，並阻止 gNB 初始化。
